<p><br /><font size="-1">The following statement explains our policy regarding the personal information we collect about you.</font></p>
<a name="top"></a>
<font size="-1"><ol>
	<li><a href="#1">Introduction</a></li>
	<li><a href="#2">Visitor Information</a></li>
