<h2><font size="-1"><a name="9">9.</a> How to see your cookie code</font></h2>
<p><font size="-1">Just click on a cookie to open it. You'll see a short string of text and numbers. The numbers are your identification card, which can only be seen by the server that gave you the cookie. <small><a href="#top">[Top]</a></small></font></p>

